{"tid":93721,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"無敵不朽既漫畫，達爾大冒險","createTime":"2017-01-24T15:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T06:56:57.000Z","uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf1cc34895b373f47a82d31bb7a6c3d2237d3a7","tid":93721,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"［img]<a href=\"http://image-4.verycd.com/edea06b1fc388dd5e0ab208ce712ae9717472/post-304485-1159623103.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage-4.verycd.com%2Fedea06b1fc388dd5e0ab208ce712ae9717472%2Fpost-304485-1159623103.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=5%2Fc7HLhlv3LDDXG6ZXhyqpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=7c67d9ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://image-4.verycd.com/edea06b1fc388dd5e0ab208ce712ae9717472/post-304485-1159623103.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n已經重睇左三次，每次都覺得，呢套野真係必睇之作，唔睇真係遺憾<br />\n嚴格上我認為，龍珠，幽白，星矢，咩一系列王道漫畫都係佢之下<br />\n呢套先係真正最強不朽既神作，睇過既人會明白我講乜"},{"pid":"3feeaf9150991da50efc23b8da37efee70f3832a","tid":93721,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:47:43.000Z","msg":"中學雞果陣睇過小說"},{"pid":"6ab8b5fe65287834a6be2782a423d11b0ab5bec2","tid":93721,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學雞果陣睇過小說</blockquote><br />\n未睇過小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊度有"},{"pid":"e1714d619e51e69a855b42ea08d500db997bdd76","tid":93721,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"套野應該叫阿布大冒險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n士兵變最強象棋那下都好型"},{"pid":"443d09c30bca247e66c9570e7d97e35495c84b28","tid":93721,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:40:08.000Z","msg":"真係好睇，我好想搵返類似既rpg王道漫睇下，但近年真係冇乜呢類漫睇了"},{"pid":"2490347b3c7d94791827288fefd21409f4c45246","tid":93721,"uid":43545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T0